subdivision, that evidence includes a resolution or ordinance of the governing authority and
for private entities, that evidence includes authorization to enter into a binding commitment
for repayment accompanied by evidence of the recommendation, permitting, or approval of
the project by a certifying department.
Present law provides for the process for publication of notice for the issuance of bonds
